msgSnippet: Hi Sally, The clue is in Shavian (and I haven t really played around with Shavian very much), but my translation is as follows: Latitude is 43 degrees and 18
messageBody:
Hi Sally,

The clue is in Shavian (and I haven't really played around with
Shavian very much), but my translation is as follows:

Latitude is 43 degrees and 18 point 493 minutes. Longitude is 84
degrees and zero point 522 minutes. Please don't trample the flowers
in your search for the cache and watch out for bees.

A quick check on the TerraServer site showes that the lat/long
coordinates are indeed in Michigan, so it might be a good translation.

I took my son on a few geocaches -- they're great fun.

Good Luck,
Jeff Smith

> thanks
